$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.If you think you’ve caught something impressive, talk to me.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiAnDe.Rockfish and seaperch are for kids. A real man catches a fighting fish... like a tuna!");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFrOp.You’re a fast learner. Here’s a few more bucks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.Simply catching any old fish isn’t going to cut it. If you want to impress me, catch a 3lb seaperch.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.3lbs? Is that it? I’ve caught bigger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.Seaperch was a warm up. To get to the next level, catch a 6lb rockfish.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.Enough with the baby fish. Time to catch something with size. Can you catch a 40lb tuna?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Sounds big. But I can handle it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.So you can catch some food fish. Now it’s time to catch something with teeth. Can you catch a 30lb hammerhead shark?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.I caught a hammerhead. It wasn’t so tough.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.I can do it. I’m not scared.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaDe.If you really want to impress me. You need to catch the king of sportfish. Catch a 50lb marlin.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.A tough sportfish. But I caught one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaDe.Ok. You’ve got skills. But do you have any world records? The world record seaperch is 5lbs. Can you beat it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.Consider me a record holder. I’ve caught one bigger than that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeAnDe.Sounds tough. But I can do it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlEx.So you’re a record holder. Care to try and set another world record? Catch a 28lb rockfish.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiHaEx.That’s a monster dude! Here’s some cash!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaOp.I can do it if I set my mind to it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.So you’ve mastered the little fish. Let’s see if you can catch something heavy. Try fighting an 80lb tuna.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrOp.Sounds heavy. But I can handle it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlDe.You think an 80lb tuna is big? Let’s see if you can catch one of the true monsters. Catch a 600lb hammerhead shark.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlDe.Damn Bro. You’ve got the right stuff!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Holy shit! That isn’t going to be easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiBaEx.Hammerheads are one thing, but a true sportfish that will give you trouble will be the 300lb Marlin.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlDe.300lbs? I think I can handle that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlDe.You’ve proven yourself dude. But can you catch a maneater? Try catching a 500lb great white shark.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlOp.It wasn’t easy. But I’ve caught one even bigger than that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlEx.You’ve caught it all it Bro. The only way to impress me would be a world record tuna. Catch one at least 105lbs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx.I’m a master at breaking world records. I’ve caught one bigger than 105lbs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiHaEx.Bro! You hold 3 world records! I’m impressed.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFlEx.Ok. So you have 3 world records. Get 4 and I’ll be impressed. See if you can catch a 1000lb hammerhead shark.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.It was the battle of a lifetime. But I landed one over 1000lbs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiHaOp.You’ve got some mad skills bro. I’m very impressed!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Can I even reel in a fish that big?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFrOp.Wow dude. You can catch a big marlin. You’ve earned some cash.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JiFrEx.Welcome to the bait shop Bro. My name’s Jim.");
